---
title: Chilli Ginger Prawns with Pear Slaw & Crushed Peanuts
description: Fresh prawns are popping with ginger and chilli, spiced to your liking, in this bowl of sweet pear slaw to balance it out. To make dinner really standout, sprinkle over peanuts for a burst of nuttiness.

